content: I'm excited to try out these seasonings and spices on my roasted vegetables this weekend. I'll definitely keep in mind to start with small amounts and taste as I go. By the way, have you heard about the new coffee shop that delivers coffee and pastries to my office building? I got a cappuccino and a chocolate croissant one morning, which was around $5. The coffee was strong and rich, and the croissant was flaky and buttery.
